WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.366
How to apply for a Knox Guard account.

2
00:00:02.366 --> 00:00:07.432
As a new Knox Guard customer, the first step is to connect with a Samsung account rep.

3
00:00:07.433 --> 00:00:11.713
They'll guide you in selecting the domain that best aligns with your business requirements

4
00:00:11.713 --> 00:00:14.465
and configure your account for optimal functionality. 

5
00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:18.999
If you don't already have a Knox Guard account rep, you can go to samsungknox.com

6
00:00:18.999 --> 00:00:20.432
and click Contact Sales.

7
00:00:20.933 --> 00:00:25.399
Once your account rep is assigned, you can begin the Knox Guard registration process. 

8
00:00:25.566 --> 00:00:29.466
Start by visiting samsungknox.com and clicking Get started.

9
00:00:29.633 --> 00:00:34.099
On the next page, click Try Samsung Knox services, then click Next. 

10
00:00:34.733 --> 00:00:39.231
On the product selection page, click Knox Guard, then click Next.

11
00:00:39.232 --> 00:00:43.977
On the following page, register your company using a Samsung account for Business.

12
00:00:43.977 --> 00:00:47.765
If you're new to Samsung Knox, you'll need to sign up for a new account.

13
00:00:48.066 --> 00:00:50.677
For a detailed walkthrough of the sign-up process, 

14
00:00:50.678 --> 00:00:54.632
check out our "Getting started with Samsung account for Business" how-to video.

15
00:00:54.733 --> 00:00:58.087
If you've already signed up for a Samsung account for Business,

16
00:00:58.088 --> 00:00:59.366
you can click Sign in.

17
00:01:00.066 --> 00:01:02.578
After you've signed up for Samsung account for Business, 

18
00:01:02.578 --> 00:01:04.665
you'll need to apply for Knox services.

19
00:01:05.133 --> 00:01:09.133
Once you complete the application and agree to the Knox Guard terms and conditions, 

20
00:01:09.133 --> 00:01:11.066
you'll be prompted to select a domain.

21
00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:13.819
Click Get started to proceed,

22
00:01:13.819 --> 00:01:16.180
then carefully review the available options and 

23
00:01:16.181 --> 00:01:19.199
choose the domain that best suits your business needs.

24
00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:20.701
Important!

25
00:01:20.701 --> 00:01:24.665
Domain selections are permanent and cannot be changed after registration.

26
00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:27.359
After confirming your domain selection,

27
00:01:27.359 --> 00:01:30.999
your application will be sent to the Samsung Knox team for approval.

28
00:01:31.166 --> 00:01:34.896
You'll receive an email confirmation once your application is approved.

29
00:01:34.897 --> 00:01:38.572
If you also signed up for Samsung account for Business during this process, 

30
00:01:38.572 --> 00:01:42.166
you must wait for a Samsung admin to approve your company's registration.

31
00:01:42.633 --> 00:01:44.248
Once everything is approved, 

32
00:01:44.248 --> 00:01:47.462
you can log into the Knox Guard console and begin utilizing

33
00:01:47.463 --> 00:01:50.065
its features to secure and manage your devices.

34
00:01:50.800 --> 00:01:54.264
To learn more about Knox Guard domains, see our other videos in the series,

35
00:01:54.264 --> 00:01:57.732
or check out our documentation at docs.samsungknox.com.

36
00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.400
Thanks for watching!

